issue.body:
*Issue #, if available:*
This is a draft.

*Description of changes:*

This changes adds a new field DisableProfiler in ProfilerConfig. It also disables the default profiler rules. The changes can be merged after the service package changes are deployed.

*Testing done:*
All the relevant unit/integration tests are updated accordingly to reflect the changes.

issue.title: add general exception to filter
issue.body:
Right now the sagemaker training toolkit only log error messages if we found certain error keyword in the logs.
We are missing general exception in the filter to log error messages. 
This PR adds that, right now we are filtering (general python exceptions, MPI errors, SageMaker library specific errors).

In future, we should extend this to custom exceptions and low level/C++ exceptions.

Right now the sagemaker training toolkit only log error messages if we found certain error keyword in the logs.
We are missing general exception in the filter to log error messages.

issue.title: add general exception to filter
issue.body:
Right now the sagemaker training toolkit only log error messages if we found certain error keyword in the logs.
We are missing general exception in the filter to log error messages. 
This PR adds that, right now we are filtering (general python exceptions, MPI errors, SageMaker library specific errors).

In future, we should extend this to custom exceptions and low level/C++ exceptions.

issue.title: add general exception to filter
issue.body:
Right now the sagemaker training toolkit only log error messages if we found certain error keyword in the logs.
We are missing general exception in the filter to log error messages. 
This PR adds that, right now we are filtering (general python exceptions, MPI errors, SageMaker library specific errors).

In future, we should extend this to custom exceptions and low level/C++ exceptions.
